<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="hero__title">For Indian sports & fitness manufacturers</h1>
    <p class="hero__subtitle">
      Reach global buyers—fitness brands, sports retailers, and ecommerce sellers—who are actively sourcing gym equipment, cricket gear, yoga products, and fitness accessories from India.
    </p>
    <%= link_to "Become a supplier", signup_path, class: "btn btn--primary btn--lg" %>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--alt">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section__title">Why join Amara India</h2>
    <p class="section__subtitle">We’re building the gateway for Indian sports and fitness manufacturing to reach the world.</p>
    <ul class="benefits-list">
      <li><strong>Global buyer reach</strong> — Your profile is visible to international brands and retailers searching for gym equipment, sports gear, and fitness product manufacturers.</li>
      <li><strong>Transparent profiles</strong> — Showcase factory location, products, MOQ, export countries, certifications, and capacity. Stand out with verification.</li>
      <li><strong>Direct inquiries</strong> — Receive quote requests and connect with serious buyers. No commission on introductions—we’re building a platform, not a broker model.</li>
      <li><strong>Future AI and expansion</strong> — As we add AI tools and new industries, verified sports and fitness suppliers will be at the center of the platform.</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-center" style="margin-top: 2rem;">
      <%= link_to "Apply to list your company", signup_path, class: "btn btn--primary btn--lg" %>
    </p>
    <p class="text-center" style="margin-top: 1.5rem; font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--color-text-muted);">
      Questions? <a href="mailto:team@amaraindia.com">team@amaraindia.com</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section__title">Supplier onboarding</h2>
    <p class="section__subtitle">Register your company to get verified and start receiving buyer inquiries.</p>
    <div class="onboarding-form">
      <form action="#" method="post">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="company">Company name</label>
          <input type="text" id="company" name="company" required placeholder="Your company name">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="email">Business email</label>
          <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required placeholder="you@company.com">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="industry">Primary category</label>
          <select id="industry" name="industry">
            <option value="">Select category</option>
            <option value="gym-equipment">Gym Equipment</option>
            <option value="sports-equipment">Sports Equipment</option>
            <option value="cricket">Cricket Gear</option>
            <option value="training">Training Equipment</option>
            <option value="fitness-accessories">Fitness Accessories</option>
            <option value="yoga">Yoga Equipment</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="message">Tell us about your products (optional)</label>
          <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="4" placeholder="Main products, export experience, certifications, capacity..."></textarea>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn--primary btn--lg btn--full">Submit</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
